# Commit Workflow

## Before Every Commit

1. Update `docs/jax_migration_plan.md` if the changes complete or advance a phase
2. Update `.cursor/rules/project-overview.mdc` if new files were added
3. Update `README.md` if a major milestone was reached

## Commit Message Format

Conventional commits: `<type>(<scope>): <description>`

Types: `feat`, `fix`, `docs`, `test`, `refactor`, `style`, `chore`

## Checklist

- [ ] `uv run pytest tests/` passes
- [ ] New distributions have: docstring with math, test config, notebook
- [ ] No debug print statements
- [ ] Type hints on all public methods
